        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜關稅風暴之最高法院 Vs 特朗普　三大指數go go go",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜關稅風暴之最高法院 Vs 特朗普 三大指數go go go\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"657\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0iqyNnbD8ZspQQUnXaPA7A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1Nw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/e34b1800-0ea8-11f1-8eff-02c058c82446\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜關稅風暴之最高法院 Vs 特朗普 三大指數go go go</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月20日，星期五。美國總統特朗普很忙，有關他的新聞全日停不了。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當然最影響全球經濟，肯定是美國最高法院以6比3裁定，推翻特朗普大規模全球關稅措施，認為他去年4月援引《國際緊急經濟權力法》向多個貿易夥伴徵收關稅時，超越總統權限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息公布後，股市扭轉早段走勢上揚，標普500指數上升近 0.7%，道指上升約 0.5%。以科技股為主的納斯達克綜合指數領漲，上升近 0.9%。三大指數均錄得全周升幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">惟特朗普又點會就此算數，即日舉行記者會上，指政府將推出「10% 全球關稅」，以取代被高院推翻的相關關稅措施。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7b44ee42-f8d5-467a-8ba5-ac5c7b5ae209-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">呢場關稅戰，依然有排打。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月20日（星期五）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 升230.81點或0.47%，報49,625.97點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 升47.62點或0.69%，報6,909.51點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 升203.34點或0.9%，報22,886.07點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約3月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約3月期油</ins></a> 收報66.31美元一桶，跌0.09美元或0.14%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,116美元一盎司，升118.6美元或2.37%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報67,725.75美元, 升630.27美元或0.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.086厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全面關稅或將取消，消息帶動電商平台股價上升，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>(AMZN.US)升2.6%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:拼多多;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/PDD/\">拼多多</a>(PDD.US)升2.9%、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Ebay;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/EBAY/\">Ebay</a>(EBAY.US)升近4%，加拿大電商Shopify(SHOP.US)升1.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國經濟分析局資料顯示，美國個人消費支出(PCE)物價指數去年12月按月上漲0.4%，為自2月以來的最大增幅，高於市場預期的0.3%，此前11月上漲0.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行策略師Michael Hartnett發表報告指，今年至今，全球股票基金每流入100美元資金，僅26美元流向美國股票，是自2020年以來的最低比例，而2022年高峰曾達到92%。報告指出，數據顯示美國例外論或持續優異表現的主題正在結束，流入美國資產的相對數量減少，而不是資金的直接流出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一則「侵訊」。美國總統特朗普計劃於3月31日至4月2日訪問中國，與中國國家主席習近平會晤。雙方料將就再度陷入不確定性的中美貿易關係，以及台灣問題相關緊張局勢進行磋商。特朗普預期此行將獲高規格禮遇，規模或超越自己於2017年首個總統任期內訪京安排。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下周見。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-vs-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8go-go-go-221335420.html",
